What a vibrant September!
<br><br>
This month, we are welcoming five new members to our community who will 
enrich our knowledge and our library of use cases.  The CloudBand 
Ecosystem now counts 49 members of different sizes and technologies. 
<br><br>
The ecosystem just returned from the Intel Developer Forum where we 
showed a powerful NFV demo. We took one of our LTE Cells and one of our 
CloudBand Nodes from our Cloud Innovation Center and shipped them to San
 Francisco and demonstrated the process of deploying and provisioning a 
vEPC and vIMS while enabling both data and HD voice calls with two 
simple clicks. CloudBand received two awards, the first for best cloud 
solution, and the second for best in show. Thanks to Intel for the 
recognition. You can read more below.
<br><br>
Meet us at our next event <a href="http://www.layer123.com/sdn" _label="OpenflowConference">SDN &amp; OpenFlow World Congress</a> in October 2014, in Dusseldorf!
<br><br>
