<strong>Whose neck do I ring? Developing accountable service quality metrics for NFV</strong>
<br><br>
Acceptable user service quality from virtualized network functions 
depends on acceptable service quality from the underlying NFV 
infrastructure; when user service quality becomes unacceptable, how do 
you know if the problem is in the VNF software or the underlying NFV 
infrastructure?
<br><br>
In this webinar, Eric Bauer, Cloud Expert and Reliability Engineer in 
the Platforms Group at Alcatel-Lucent will review the key service 
quality metrics of NFV infrastructure, management and orchestration that
 impact application service quality delivered to end users.
<br><br>
